    "Id": "155907",
    "ThreadId": "46170",
    "Html": "Try this....<br>\r\n<br>\r\n        &lt;toolkit:DataGrid&gt;<br>\r\n            &lt;toolkit:DataGrid.Resources&gt;<br>\r\n                &lt;Style TargetType=&quot;{x:Type primitives:DataGridColumnHeader}&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n                    &lt;Setter Property=&quot;HorizontalContentAlignment&quot; Value=&quot;Stretch&quot; /&gt;<br>\r\n                    &lt;Setter Property=&quot;ContentTemplate&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n                        &lt;Setter.Value&gt;<br>\r\n                            &lt;DataTemplate&gt;<br>\r\n                                &lt;StackPanel&gt;<br>\r\n                                    &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{Binding}&quot;/&gt;<br>\r\n                                    &lt;TextBox /&gt;<br>\r\n                                &lt;/StackPanel&gt;<br>\r\n                            &lt;/DataTemplate&gt;<br>\r\n                        &lt;/Setter.Value&gt;<br>\r\n                    &lt;/Setter&gt;<br>\r\n                &lt;/Style&gt;<br>\r\n            &lt;/toolkit:DataGrid.Resources&gt;<br>\r\n        &lt;/toolkit:DataGrid&gt;\r\n",
